snippet.title: Star Wars Jedi Knight: Mysteries of the Sith -Addon- (Gameplay).
snippet.description:
Star Wars Jedi Knight: Mysteries of the Sith was released in 1998.
Published by Lucas Arts.
USK rated this game 18.

Mysteries of the Sith is the Add-on to Jedi Knight 1.
It adds new levels and new charaters.

BTW: I used the following cheats:
diediedie = All Weapons
boinga 1 = God Mode
freebird = You can "fly"

I must use them, cause like at 00:48 it was hard to get to that part without use the fly cheat.
